Correspondence table between German postcodes and NUTS level 3 codes

Source: R/nuts_de.R
nuts_de.Rd

Correspondence table between German postcodes and NUTS level 3 codes

Usage

nuts_de

Format

An object of class spec_tbl_df (inherits from tbl_df, tbl, data.frame) with 8320 rows and 2 columns.

Source

"© European Union - GISCO, 2021, postal code point dataset, Licence CC-BY-SA 4.0 available at https://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/web/gisco/geodata/reference-data."

Examples

nuts_de
